oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Photograph of Virgil Metcalf and fellow WWI soldiers
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Inducted in McMinn County, TN and possibly taken at Camp Sheridan in Montgomery, Alabama, the photo shows Pvt. Metcalf of Co. A, 47th Engineering Battn. and a couple of fellow trainees outside camp tents. He received an honorable discharge in 1919.
